- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes an AI-based approach to approximate Graph Edit Distance. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper deals with the problem of computing Graph Edit Distance, which is a fundamental problem in graph theory and algorithms. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper proposes a method for comparing and matching sets of nodes in graphs, which can be seen as a language-related task.
